OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773857158
OL,3,C'If Liverpool fans are unhappy with me
OL,4,CI must have done things wrong'
OL,6,FLiverpool head coach Arne Slot says he
OL,7,Frealises "must have done a lot of
OL,8,Fthings wrong" as he aims to get
OL,9,Ffrustrated fans back onside.
OL,11,FThe team were booed off after
OL,12,Fconceding a 90th-minute equaliser to
OL,13,FTottenham on 15 March - the first time
OL,14,Fthe Premier League-winning Dutchman
OL,15,Fhas had such an adverse reaction at
OL,16,FAnfield since arriving in the summer
OL,17,Fof 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
