PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773857158
OL,3,C'If Liverpool fans are unhappy with me
OL,4,CI must have done things wrong'
OL,6,FIt is the first time fans have
OL,7,Fexpressed their feelings so publicly
OL,8,Fmirroring the anti-Slot mood on social
OL,9,Fmedia which has been growing for some
OL,10,Ftime during a poor season.
OL,12,F"It's never nice they are frustrated
OL,13,Fbecause usually fans are not
OL,14,Ffrustrated after you win," Slot said
OL,15,Fahead of their Champions League last-
OL,16,F16 second leg against Galatasaray, in
OL,17,Fwhich they must overturn a 1-0 deficit.
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773857158
OL,3,C'If Liverpool fans are unhappy with me
OL,4,CI must have done things wrong'
OL,6,F"People told me when I came here that
OL,7,Fthey will support the manager for such
OL,8,Fa long time, but (if) you are
OL,9,Fsupposing something then I must have
OL,10,Fdone a lot of things wrong.
OL,12,F"That's never a nice feeling to have
OL,13,Fbecause being in the club that's
OL,14,Falways so supportive for the manager,
OL,15,Fin good and bad times, then if they
OL,16,Fare not happy with me, then apparently
OL,17,FI've done so many things wrong.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773857158
OL,3,C'If Liverpool fans are unhappy with me
OL,4,CI must have done things wrong'
OL,6,F"I did something wrong in the season
OL,7,Fthat we won the league and I
OL,8,Fdefinitely did maybe make a few
OL,9,Fdecisions that were not perfect in
OL,10,Fhindsight.
OL,12,F"But all the decisions I've made, I've
OL,13,Falways made for the same reason, for
OL,14,Fus trying to win the game.
OL,16,F"But I also know how the football
OL,17,Findustry works. Winning can change a
OL,18,Flot. That's what we are trying to
OL,19,Fachieve tomorrow and we're completely
OL,20,Fready for that."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU|D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
