PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773857158
OL,3,C'If Liverpool fans are unhappy with me
OL,4,CI must have done things wrong'
OL,6,FIn an analysis piece on Sky Sports
OL,7,Fformer Reds defender Jamie Carragher
OL,8,Fsaid Liverpool were a "team of
OL,9,Findividuals" and that was why the game
OL,10,Fplan was not working.
OL,12,FReacting to the comments, Slot, who
OL,13,Fhad not seen the clip, said: "If he
OL,14,Fmeans we are not perfectly playing
OL,15,Ftogether in ball possession and off
OL,16,Fthe ball then he is right.
OL,26,@pD@WOUqD@LO]uD@^OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773857158
OL,3,C'If Liverpool fans are unhappy with me
OL,4,CI must have done things wrong'
OL,6,F"It is not like we are 11 individuals
OL,7,F- if he meant that then I completely
OL,8,Fdisagree. That is nothing to do with
OL,9,Fan individual mentality, but that the
OL,10,Fconnections are not as strong yet.
OL,12,F"I agree with a lot of things Jamie
OL,13,Fhas said throughout this whole season.
OL,14,FThis particular one, I disagree with
OL,15,Fhim. I don't see this after we
OL,16,Fconceded for 1-1.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773857158
OL,3,C'If Liverpool fans are unhappy with me
OL,4,CI must have done things wrong'
OL,6,F"After so many disappointments, it
OL,7,Fwould not have been strange if the
OL,8,Fplayers had given up but they did not.
OL,9,FThey (Spurs) had a counter-attack
OL,10,Fwhere seven or eight of our players
OL,11,Fwere back in our 18-yard-box and we
OL,12,Fblocked the shot and the corner led to
OL,13,Fa chance all the way on the other side
OL,14,Ffor Hugo Ekitike.
OL,16,F"A team that has given up, a team of
OL,17,Findividuals or a team that does not
OL,18,Fwork together, does not show that
OL,19,Fresilience after our 120th setback
OL,20,Fthis season ` that is a bit of an
OL,21,Fexaggeration but we have had many.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
