PN,39708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773857158
OL,3,C'If Liverpool fans are unhappy with me
OL,4,CI must have done things wrong'
OL,6,F"He (Carragher) said a lot of things
OL,7,Fthroughout this season that I agree
OL,8,Fwith because I see similar. I cannot
OL,9,Falways say them and it is helpful for
OL,10,Fme to not go into detail with other
OL,11,Fones I have agreed with."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@YO]
